sql_query.sql: SELECT "product_category"."id", "product_category"."name", "product_category"."parent_id", "product_category"."lft", "product_category"."rght", "product_category"."tree_id", "product_category"."level", T2."id", T2."name", T2."parent_id", T2."lft", T2."rght", T2."tree_id", T2."level" FROM "product_category" INNER JOIN "product_category" T2 ON ("product_category"."parent_id" = T2."id") WHERE "product_category"."parent_id" IN (2)
